            "notes": "The main goal of this deck is to quickly ramp up mana and put pressure on the opponent with aggressive creatures. The deck includes a variety of mana dorks like Arbor Elf, Elvish Mystic, and Avacyn's Pilgrim to accelerate mana production. Cards like Birthing Pod and Finale of Devastation allow for tutoring and fetching key creatures from the deck. There are also protection spells like Mother of Runes and Giver of Runes to keep important creatures safe. The deck focuses on fast mana ramp, efficient creature tutoring, and aggressive plays with a mix of green and white creatures to overwhelm the opponent and secure a victory in a 1 vs 1 Duel Commander format."
